Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:50.44,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}巨大的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:55.04,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就在這裡  從此起步
