Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:03.95,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因為  這份痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:05.89,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}會讓我們通往未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:09.85,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大家齊心協力能讓自己變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:11.10,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:14.58,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不斷的變化  We'll be star!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:19.62,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果能為自己所喜歡的事加油的話
