Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.44,0:00:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上集的LOVELIVE！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以組成了偶像團體為起點的我們三人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗試挑戰了出道演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繆斯的出道演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望演唱會能夠成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  希望能大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣我們也要歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著能在全場觀眾面前高唱的一天前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽你以後想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽想當偶像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像？真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實際上…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞蹈的動作一定都記住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這裡請小泉來讀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大聲點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was be preferable by the…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡結束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才這裡開始  今井你讀下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.49,0:01:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}He gave me some…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話根本不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥最近每天都要來看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似突然對它著迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們發傳單去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一會會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有五人不被承認是社團的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法參加像樣的社團活動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脖子上毛茸茸的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥  這樣做不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就先用弓來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀  都怪你說了奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許被討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們只是在開心地和你玩罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒水了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是負責養羊駝的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是飼養員所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是來看演唱會的花陽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不敢當
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑過來看的一年生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成為偶像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果  太直接啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太耀眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕  不會讓你受委屈的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺看著像個壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不適當強硬一點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西木野同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你能再說一遍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得西木野同學很適合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌也唱的非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡她的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就去把她勸誘過來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她說絕對不要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我又說錯話了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快點體育課要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也快點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天說了今天要決定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不決定的話  大家都要開始活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那個  凜你要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田徑部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田徑嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想進偶像部試試？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？那種事…才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的  花陽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說謊的時候一定會勾著手指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會跟你一起去的  走吧  去學姐那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？真的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成為偶像什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽你這麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會出名的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是等一下  等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…能讓我任性的說兩句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法  什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我說要成為偶像的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不適合當偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我那麼男孩子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮也這麼短
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想想以前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛  凜你超適合穿裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一直穿褲子的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你有裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比誰先跑到校門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是先換一件再來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不適合當偶像什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西木野同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生完全沒聚集過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得偶像活動對音木坂學院來說有弊無利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為學校的狀況就限制學生的活動有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  為了讓學校繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請你讓學生會獨立活動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  看上去也不是一點人氣都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是之前的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是誰拍了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:09:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我是和真姬同學同班的小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在在醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家經營著醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後準備讓她繼承下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了高中以後還沒有一個朋友來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還很擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  你掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是西木野同學的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為  為什麼你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了繆斯的海報了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎  我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認錯人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  學生手冊也掉在那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  都怪你說了奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我成為校園偶像？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放學時一直在音樂室那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽西木野同學的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡到想一直聽下去  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大學已經決定要進醫學部了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說我的音樂已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我  你才想當偶像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之前的演唱會你不是看的很入迷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來西木野同學也去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我只是正好路過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做就去做不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  我也會為你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有各種各樣的苦衷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給媽媽買點點心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOVELIVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要看店  你在上面等一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能到這個程度的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒關係  我們才該說對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒想到海未居然會在練習姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都  都怪穗乃果去看店人不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你真的要來做偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是偶然過來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就請她吃點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗村特產穗村饅頭  簡稱穗饅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果  我帶電腦來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  我的老是在關鍵時候壞掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  找到影片了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒確認  估計是在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰拍的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播放數好多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼多人在看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段表演得很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡練習了很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功的時候差點想握拳大叫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  花陽  你那邊很難看清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要認真考慮下來做校園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是很適合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實也不喜歡在人前表演
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得自己不適合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有時候也會忘詞  運動神經也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很冒失的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是職業的偶像  我們肯定瞬間就不及格了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果是校園偶像的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷著一份幹勁和熱忱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以試著去做好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得那就是校園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  如果你想做的話  就試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  練習可是很嚴格的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好考慮一下  再告訴我們答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們隨時都在等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那讓身影朦朧的霧靄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}在這裡也完全地消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的話  就試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}好  到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從遠方的山上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這篇文章中與四郎的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究  究竟是什…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  下面是…佐藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這篇文章中與四郎的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西木野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的聲音其實是很好聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只有放大聲音好好練習而已了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大聲點  站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西木野同學？為什麼你在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在鼓勵我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要去學姐那裡說想做偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好別那麼催促她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她再有點自信也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼西木野同學要來管凜和花陽的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想說  要唱的話  那樣做會比較好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽總是優柔寡斷的  乾脆點決定會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  昨天和她交談後我覺得好像不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  不要吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽走吧  學姐她們要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一定要去的話  就我帶她去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於音樂我給的建議會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繆斯的歌也是我作曲的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  如果要帶的話  就讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來帶她去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人  來人救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  你想要加入我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  花陽很早以前就想當偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子唱歌挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是字面上的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你要猶豫到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是去做會比較好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的話  就試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我也說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發出聲音是很簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的  你一直以來  都想成為偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凜  西木野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  我會一直支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也說過會稍微為你加油的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫小泉花陽  一年級  人也很矮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音又小  又怕生  沒有任何特長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  可是我想做偶像的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會輸給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  請讓我加入繆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽  太了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  西木野同學也在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰哭了啊  我才沒有哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  你們兩個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個打算怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  什麼怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還在召集成員哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晨練每天都要那麼早起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你的眼鏡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我換隱形眼鏡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  很可愛  非常可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西木野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你不帶眼鏡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便直接叫我名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會直呼你們的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花陽  凜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真姬真姬真姬真姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真姬真姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞了害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真姬好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}（要談偶像還早10年！）
